---
import Container from '../shared/Container.astro'
import Paragraph from '../shared/Paragraph.astro'
---

<section class='relative'>
  <Container>
    <div class='py-24 sm:py-32'>
      <div class='mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8'>
        <div class='mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center'>
          <h2 class='text-heading-1 text-l font-bold'>
            <span
              class='text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 from-20% via-primary via-30% to-green-600'
            >
              冷たい風と青い空の調和
            </span>
          </h2>
          <p class='mt-2 text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl'>
            <Paragraph> モリーオ市の森：自然と芸術が織りなす美 </Paragraph>
          </p>

          <Paragraph className='mt-6 text-lg leading-8'>
            あのイーハトーヴォのすきとおった風、夏でも底に冷たさをもつ青いそら、うつくしい森で飾られたモリーオ市、郊外のぎらぎらひかる草の波。
          </Paragraph>
        </div>
        <div class='mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-4xl'>
